 recorded, four in Blida Province, men aged 32, 56, 72 and 73 respectively, two in S\u00e9tif Province, one in the Bordj Bou Arreridj Province, one in Oran Province and one in Tipaza Province.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.aps.dz/sante-science-technologie/103578-covid19-132-nouveaux-cas-confirmes-et-9-nouveaux-deces-enregistres-en-algerie|title=Covid19: 132 nouveaux cas confirm\u00e9s et 9 nouveaux d\u00e9c\u00e8s enregistr\u00e9s en Alg\u00e9rie|last=Nassima|first=Dib|website=www.aps.dz|language=fr-fr|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n\nOn 1 April, a total of 131 new confirmed cases of coronavirus (Covid-19) and 14 new deaths have been recorded over the last 24 hours, putting the total number of confirmed cases at 847 and that of deaths at 58.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.aps.dz/en/health-science-technology/33786-coronavirus-131-new-confirmed-cases-14-new-deaths-in-algeria|title=Coronavirus: 131 new confirmed cases, 14 new deaths in Algeria|last=CHAFAI|first=Mohamed|website=www.aps.dz|language=en-gb|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref> New deaths have been recorded, five in Algiers, and three in Blida Province, one in Relizane Province, one Gharda\u00efa Province, one in  Oum El Bouaghi Province, one in M\u00e9d\u00e9a Province, one in  Tizi Ouzou Province, and one  A\u00efn T\u00e9mouchent Province.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.algerie-eco.com/2020/04/01/coronavirus-846-cas-confirmes-et-14-nouveaux-deces-en-algerie/|title=Coronavirus : 847 cas confirm\u00e9s et 14 nouveaux d\u00e9c\u00e8s en Alg\u00e9rie|last=Litamine|first=Khelifa|date=2020-04-01|website=Algerie Eco|language=fr-FR|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n\nOn 2 April, A total of 139 confirmed new cases and 28 new deaths have been recorded in the last 24 hours, bringing the total number of confirmed cases to 986 and that of deaths to 86. The new deaths were recorded in the provinces of Blida (5), Algiers (5), Setif (4), Medea (4), and one death in the provinces of Tiaret, Ain Defla, Oran, Relizane, Mostaganem, Oum El Bouaghi, Bejaia,Tipaza, Boumerdes and Batna.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.aps.dz/en/health-science-technology/33794-coronavirus-986-confirmed-cases-83-deaths-in-algeria|title=Coronavirus: 986 confirmed cases, 83 deaths in Algeria|last=Sidhoum|first=Samira|website=www.aps.dz|language=en-gb|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n\n== Location of cases ==\n{| class=\"wikitable centre alternance sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n!scope=\"col\"| Province\n!scope=\"col\"| First case\n!scope=\"col\"| Confirmed cases\n!scope=\"col\"| Deaths\n!scope=\"col\"| Recoveries\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Blida Province|Blida]]\n| 1 March 2020\n| 385\n| 22\n| 29\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Algiers Province|Algiers]]\n| 13 March 2020\n| 154\n| 14\n| 11\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Oran Province|Oran]]\n|21 March 2020\n|62\n|3\n|0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Tizi Ouzou Province|Tizi Ouzou]]\n|12 March 2020\n| 40\n| 5\n| 2\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[B\u00e9ja\u00efa Province|B\u00e9ja\u00efa]]\n|17 March 2020<ref name=\":3\" /><ref name=\":4\" />\n| 36\n| 2\n| 1\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Tipaza Province|Tipaza]]\n|22 March 2020\n|27\n|5\n|0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[S\u00e9tif Province|S\u00e9tif]]\n| 19 March 2020\n| 25\n| 8\n| 2\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[M\u00e9d\u00e9a Province|M\u00e9d\u00e9a]]\n|18 March 2020\n| 22\n| 7\n| 1\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Ain Defla Province|Ain Defla]]\n|24 March 2020\n|20\n|2\n|0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Mostaganem Province|Mostaganem]]\n|25 March 2020\n|20\n|1\n|1\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[El Oued Province|El Oued]]\n|18 March 2020\n| 16\n| 2\n| 1\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Tlemcen Province|Tlemcen]]\n|23 March 2020\n|16\n|0\n|0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Skikda Province|Skikda]]\n| 12 March 2020\n| 13\n| 0\n| 3\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Batna Province|Batna]]\n|25 March 2020\n|12\n|1\n|0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Bordj Bou Arr\u00e9ridj Province|Bordj Bou Arr\u00e9ridj]]\n| 16 March 2020<ref name=\":3\" />\n| 12\n| 2\n| 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Boumerd\u00e8s Provin